  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, we defined the scope of our meeting to include only human-generated feedback, ranging from minimal and informal approaches to in-depth formal peer reviews.",
    "The diversity of human feedback creates a need to formalize the definition of preprint review.",
    "Based on input from the two Working Groups convened in advance of the Recognizing Preprint Peer Review workshop [18, 19], the participants at the meeting defined preprint review as a subset of public preprint feedback that meets certain criteria.",
